{"pageModel":{"attributes":{"id":"","name":"106356.dita","viewName":"DitaDetail"},"elements":{"ditaContent":{"name":"DITAContent","value":"<article id=\"cisco-ai-assistant-for-security-cloud-control\" class=\"topic concept\">\r\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Cisco AI Assistant for Security Cloud Control</h1>\r\n<div class=\"body conbody\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">The Cisco AI Assistant provides intelligent automation and support for Cisco Security Cloud Control, enabling security teams to efficiently manage, troubleshoot, and optimize their security infrastructure. This document highlights the key capabilities of different AI assistants across Cisco’s security products.</p>\r\n<section class=\"section\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Cisco Firewall AI Assistant</strong>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p\">As firewalls remain a critical component of network security, managing policies, troubleshooting issues, and optimizing configurations can be complex. The Cisco Firewall AI Assistant simplifies these tasks by leveraging AI-driven insights and automation, reducing manual intervention and improving efficiency.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Key skills:</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul\">\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Documentation Assistance:</strong> Provides step-by-step answers to documentation-related queries, with citations.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Policy Inquiry &amp; Analysis:</strong> Summarizes access control policies, rule configurations, and security policies across devices.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Policy Rule Creation:</strong> Simplifies the creation of firewall access control policies via natural language commands.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Policy Optimization:</strong> Identifies anomalies and suggests improvements for access control policies.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Ticketing Integration:</strong> Allows users to open and retrieve TAC cases directly from the AI assistant.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</section>\r\n<section id=\"Cisco-Secure-Access-AI-Assistant\" class=\"section\">\r\n<h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Cisco Secure Access AI Assistant</strong>\r\n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"p\">Ensuring seamless, secure access for users and devices requires managing complex policies and troubleshooting network issues. The Cisco Secure Access AI Assistant simplifies these challenges by offering AI-driven policy creation, automated troubleshooting, and enhanced monitoring capabilities.</p>\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Key skills:</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<ul class=\"ul\">\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Policy Creation:</strong> Enables intuitive, natural language-based creation of secure access policies.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Troubleshooting Automation:</strong> Diagnoses private application access failures through structured analysis.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">\r\n<strong class=\"ph b\">Digital Experience Monitoring:</strong> Provides real-time insights via ThousandEyes integration for network and application performance.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n","ditaVal":"","format":"html"},"bookTitle":{"value":""},"shortDescription":{"value":""}}},"parameters":{"appId":"SccAiAssistant","topicAlias":"AIAssistantSCC"}}